data.title: Former Russian PM Kasyanov on Conflict Zone – DW – 08
data.meta_description: Former Prime Minister Mikhail Kasyanov, who worked under Vladimir Putin in the early 2000s, tells DW that he fears for his life — and everyone in Russia should be scared.
data.text: Conflict Zone is DW’s top political interview program. Join us each week as our hosts put tough questions to top guests from around the world. Get beyond the soundbite – enter the Conflict Zone.
